#: ../../docs/user_manual/map_views/3d_map_view.rst:170
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Skirt height`: Sometimes it is possible to see small cracks "
"between tiles of the terrain. Raising this value will add vertical walls "
"(\"skirts\") around terrain tiles to hide the cracks."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skjørtehøyde`: Noen ganger ser man små gliper mellom "
"terrengfliser. Øk denne verdien for å legge til loddrette vegger («skjørt») "
"rundt terrengflisene for å skjule glipene."

